{"tid":1618443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地需要一個battlecry!!!!!","createTime":"2019-10-04T05:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T09:38:14.000Z","uid":68219,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d15fda684681c50256f5db4ac19f7786f939d591","tid":1618443,"uid":68219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"發夢諗到d野  趁仲記得寫低先<br />\n以前曾經有人提過光復香港 時代革命做口號<br />\n721上環係我第一次見到開始多人叫 之後就一直叫到依家<br />\n<br />\n但係我一直覺得要附和果陣叫 &quot;時代革命&quot; 都幾繞口<br />\n更何況前線亂既時候根本無時間講足四隻字<br />\n<br />\n如果要踢波 / 救人 / 推上橋, 唔知有無人跟就無人帶頭<br />\n如果有種口號係和應衝既 士氣會高好多<br />\n<br />\n例如marines會係和應既時候叫OORAH<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xoD9QoLHN64\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxoD9QoLHN64&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3hVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=a58cada6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xoD9QoLHN64</a><br />\nOORAH叫起上黎易齊 又夠motvational 由肺底叫到上黎 我個人覺得係最好既battlecry之一<br />\n<br />\n試諗下金鐘天橋底準備攻上去時一大班人叫OORAH 而唔係亂咁鳩叫恐慌既光景<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申唔係想搞散光復香港時代革命 慢推時可以叫 但真係唔適合快速推進時叫<br />\n<br />\n磚已拋 希望會有屬於香港人battlecry"},{"pid":"fda8598bd2791f7b2d7ad91355c6de6b2d83a2fe","tid":1618443,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"g chi"},{"pid":"d3a0cacb320d7b094fe42eaaf7b25e202987aa0d","tid":1618443,"uid":68219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:20:57.000Z","msg":"OORAH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e256739f8825bc0c95d5141ead1a83d6c3441c","tid":1618443,"uid":9394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:21:38.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗？"},{"pid":"227daeeb8264fc05cc0b5ddf43ce1d608080f6b4","tid":1618443,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cl